name: Cone Ring Worm v2
description: Cone Ring Worm v2 is a looping video by Sunny Nestler, made in 2021. The iconic cone worm first appeared in Nestler’s work around 2010. A common everyday symbol, the traffic cone tells us very plainly where we can’t go; typically cones linked together are perceived as barriers. But when transformed into organic, segmented creatures they come to life, showing where you can go! See more of Nestler’s work here: http://www.megaspora.space
